spiritual path and be true to yourself as this allows you to concentrate on your authentic self, rather than on superficial issues and distractions. Put your focus on believing that you will achieve positive results in all aspects of your life, and put your energy into taking positive action towards achieving your goals. Expect positive results and you will receive positive results.\tLive your life with passion and\tpurpose\tand allow miracles to happen in your life.\tNumber 2047 relates to\tnumber 4\t(2+0+4+7=13, 1+3=4) and\tAngel Number 4\t.\t*\tJoanne Walmsley\tSacred Scribes\tNUMEROLOGY\t  -  The Vibration and Energy of Numbers\tANGELS ARCHANGELS and ASCENDED MASTERS"
